<section class="page-careers">
  <div class="page-content__inner">

    <p class="page-content__eyebrow">Opportunities</p>
    <h1 class="page-content__title">Careers</h1>
    <p class="page-content__subtitle">Build something real.</p>

    <div class="page-content__body">
      <p>Hyper Real Love is a small team building a brand that believes in working on your Self. We are not a startup scaling for growth. We are practitioners building tools, anchors, and community for people ready to live more intentionally.</p>

      <p>We move slowly and deliberately. Every piece of content, every cap, every Journal Club session is made with care. If that resonates with you, we want to know.</p>

      <p><strong>We're open to contributions in:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Brand &amp; creative direction</li>
        <li>Community building &amp; events</li>
        <li>Writing &amp; editorial</li>
        <li>Design &amp; visual identity</li>
        <li>Development &amp; technology</li>
        <li>Photography &amp; film</li>
      </ul>

      <p>There are no open roles in the traditional sense. If you want to contribute to Hyper Real Love, send us a proposal. Tell us what you would do and why it matters to you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="page-content__cta">
      <p class="page-content__cta-label">Send your proposal to</p>
      <a href="mailto:info@hyperreallove.com" class="page-content__email-link">info@hyperreallove.com</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

